// Maqam Rast — Arabic quarter-tone scale
// Arabic music uses French solfège names (do re mi fa sol la si)
// but with quarter-tone intervals from the maqam system

@core
@controls
@alphabet.arabic:browser
@tuning:maqam_rast
@mm:70

S -> Sayr Rujoo Qarar

Sayr -> do re mi fa sol la si (wave:sine, vel:85)
Rujoo -> si la sol fa mi re do (vel:70)
Qarar -> do _ _ _ _ (vel:60)
